components.description:
1-cell Li-Po/Li-Ion battery charger IC (MCP73831T-2ACI)

Cut out the jumper on the back side, and solder to set the charging current (default 100mA)

1-cell Li-Po/Li-Ion battery fuel gauge IC (MAX17048)

Conected to D (SDA), C (SCL), and LIPO_ALERT (IO16) pins
3.3v LDO for ESP32-S3 and QWIIC modules

3.3v LDO for Slot modules

Set low voltage to pin EN_SLOT (IO15) for power off all Slot modules

Power status led

Cut out the jumper on the back side to disable power status led

Li-Po/Li-Ion battery charging status led

Cut out the jumper on the back side to disable charging status led

User led (IO21)

Cut out the jumper on the back side to disable User led

QWIIC connector

Cut out the jumper on the back side to disable I²C Pull-Up resistors

USB-C Port (500mA)

D+ and D- conected to ESP32-S3 USB OTG or Internal USB Serial / JTAG (IO20 (D+), IO19 (D-))
